snippet.title: Fate Arena - Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Fate Arena - a strategic multiplayer battle arena featuring over 50 unique characters and 8 arenas to climb. Will you be the King of the Arena? 

Summer 2019 is finally here :P

Join Discord.gg/FateArena for launch details. The game will release this week in soft launch. Select regions for mobile.

Soft launching in select regions on soon. Rolling out on iOS, Google Play and Steam (PC).
